::Cygnar::
       He stopped quite a distance from the Tripred base, he was only close 
enough to get general numbers and sizes of active bots.  He scanned while 
circling in the air and flew back to the base.  Landing outside of 
Galvatron's ship he transformed and walked in.  He walks up to Galvatron and 
Starstorm.  He taps Galvatron on the shoulder.  "Oh fearless leader.  I've 
returned with the data you requested.  I only got general information.  There 
are six or seven of them, two maybe three are large and probably well armed.  
Anything further and you'll have to infiltrate."

--part1_190.996893b.2a5e732f_boundary
